\small{\$ git merge branchA \textit{(merge branchA into branchB)}}
\small{\textit{(merge and squash all commits of branchA into branchB)}}
\small{\$ git branch "[brach name]"} \textit{(create a new branch)}
\small{\$ git checkout -b "[brach name]"} \textit{(create a new branch and switch to it)}
